item.title: Squarepusher
item.description: Tom Jenkinson, known professionally as Squarepusher, is an English electronic musician, record producer, bassist, and DJ. His music spans several genres, including drum and bass, IDM, jazz, and electroacoustic music. His recordings are often typified by a combination of complex drum programming, live instrumental playing, and digital signal processing. Since 1995, he has recorded for Warp Records as well as smaller labels. He released 1996 debut LP Feed Me Weird Things on Rephlex Records.
